gw.bizrules.pcf

Class LookupExpressionFragmentHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.bizrules.pcf.ExpressionFragmentHolder<T,java.lang.Object>
      • gw.bizrules.pcf.ConditionExpressionFragmentHolder<LookupExpressionFragment>
        • gw.bizrules.pcf.LookupExpressionFragmentHolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NestedInputConfig, ScopedValidatable

    public class LookupExpressionFragmentHolder
extends ConditionExpressionFragmentHolder<LookupExpressionFragment>
    LookupExpressionFragmentHolder is a conditional expression holder for creating lookup expression fragment when the user selected lookup option from Rule Condition line or from a rule variable.
